                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <h3>
                            Recent Interest<br /><small>Microsoft MVC</small>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p class="lead">
                        I've recently acquired a taste for web development and am in the process of testing out Microsoft's MVC technology.
                        Combined with the power of <a href="http://www.getbootstrap.com">Bootstrap</a> and <a href="https://jquery.com/">jQuery</a>,
                        I aim to produce lightning fast, responsive websites designed to deliver robust and relevant content.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
